text: Pseudorimula is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Lepetodrilidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Pseudorimula include: * Pseudorimula marianae McLean, 1989 * Pseudorimula midatlantica McLean, 1992 ==References== ==External links== Category:Lepetodrilidae
title: Pseudorimula
